{"tid":1295133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行蹤紀錄】7.7晚尖沙咀有人男扮女裝不斷影大頭相","createTime":"2019-07-08T02:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T02:55:25.000Z","uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9beed8caf3693aed6f03dac7bb9b35ff8c6f4ed","tid":1295133,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:33:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n尋日去完九龍大遊行<br />\n行完就走（因為屋企人係藍絲，所以我都唔可以留太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n去到柯士甸站<br />\n大約5點半左右準備上一班前往紅磡嘅列車<br />\n（我遊行完有check時間，所以我記得時間地點）<br />\n<br />\n跟住見到一個人落車<br />\n著住OL裝，但係眉頭眼額真係唔似女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比較似係麻甩佬帶假髮<br />\n（我當時相當訝異，亦有其他途人側目，所以印象好深刻）<br />\n嗰陣時已經懷疑係咪有人男扮女裝，不過以為自己多心<br />\n<br />\n點知今朝睇返蘋果尋晚直播<br />\n屌真係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dck0Ddt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDck0Ddt.jpg&h=71fc11a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無手足尋日下午搭車走嘅時候同我一樣見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8891805f96a822df1ab57d47cbf40904a47c8acd","tid":1295133,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:35:56.000Z","msg":"留意返<br />\n我嘅重點唔係在於當事人嘅裝束/性別認同之類<br />\n而係我問返有睇直播嘅朋友<br />\n佢地話當事人 //據聞自稱蘋果記者。後蘋果直播抵達，該名人士<span style=\"color: gold;\">拒絕出示記者證</span>。//"},{"pid":"b99003f3de6059464b3c5b0e36d558cc8bb7a501","tid":1295133,"uid":22116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"睇佢右手手指 99%男人"},{"pid":"fd7051663071087b4976f45fc13af25785c3acd3","tid":1295133,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"係咪大公記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7678b08